data.oai_dc:dc: Descriptive statistics for upper and lower cheek teeth of Archaeopithecus rogeri considering three levels of wear.

Supplemental Data 3. Descriptive statistics for upper and lower cheek teeth of Archaeopithecus rogeri considering three levels of wear. SW (stage of wear) = 1, little, 2, middle, 3, heavy (see text for details). CV (coefficient of variation) = 100 × (SD/mean). Measurements in mm.
